*Vatru* je čovek prvi put otkrio pre hiljadu godina. (Man discovered fire for the first time a thousand years ago.)

Njegovo lice je bilo obasjano *vatrom* radosti. (His face was illuminated by the fire of joy.)

On je došao do *vatre* preko suhih grančica. (He came to the fire by means of dry twigs.)

Ona je držala lulu u ruci i njeno meso je zračilo *vatrom*. (She held a hookah in her hand and her flesh radiated fire.)

Oni su gledali u *vatru* u očekivanju čuda. (They looked into the fire in expectation of a miracle.)